OL,3,CWales and Lions great Barry John dies
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,FJohn, who was nicknamed The King by
OL,7,FNew Zealand journalists after he
OL,8,Finspired the Lions' famous 1971 Test
OL,9,Fseries victory over the All Blacks,
OL,10,Fwon 25 Wales caps between 1966 and
OL,11,F1972.
OL,13,FHe also played in five Tests on their
OL,14,F1968 and 1971 tours, before retiring
OL,15,Ffrom rugby at the age of 27.
OL,17,FA statement released by John's family
OL,18,Fread: "Barry John died peacefully
OL,19,Ftoday at the University Hospital of
OL,20,FWales surrounded by his loving wife
OL,21,Fand four children.
