OL,3,CWales and Lions great Barry John dies
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,F"He was a loving dad to his 11
OL,7,Fgrandchildren and much-loved brother."
OL,9,FJohn played his club rugby for
OL,10,FLlanelli and then Cardiff, where he
OL,11,Fstruck up a half-back partnership with
OL,12,FGareth Edwards that went on to
OL,13,Fflourish for Wales and the Lions.
OL,15,FJohn was partnered by Edwards in 23 of
OL,16,Fhis Wales international appearances,
OL,17,Fplus all five Lions Tests ` one
OL,18,Fagainst South Africa and four against
OL,19,FNew Zealand.
