OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,FAnother star of Welsh rugby's golden
OL,7,Fera, full-back JPR Williams, died four
OL,8,Fweeks ago.
OL,10,FJonathan Davies, one of the most
OL,11,Frenowned Welsh players of the 1980s
OL,12,Fand 1990s, paid tribute to John,
OL,13,Fwriting on X: "RIP Barry ` another one
OL,14,Fof my heroes sadly gone.
OL,15,F_BarryJohnTheKing"
OL,17,FThe Lions added in a statement: "We
OL,18,Fare hugely saddened that the great
OL,19,FBarry John has passed away at the age
OL,20,Fof 79.
