OL,3,CWales and Lions great Barry John dies
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,F"Barry inspired so many and will
OL,7,Fforever be remembered for how much he
OL,8,Fgave to the sport."
OL,10,FWRU president Terry Cobner, who played
OL,11,Fin the Welsh back-row and toured with
OL,12,Fthe Lions in 1977, described John as
OL,13,F"probably the greatest" fly-half of
OL,14,Fall time.
OL,16,F"To be crowned 'The King' in New
OL,17,FZealand when every back row forward in
OL,18,Fboth the North and South Islands is
OL,19,Ftrying to take your head off is quite
OL,20,Fsome accolade," said Cobner.
