OL,8,Fhalves who have ever played the game `
OL,9,Fprobably the greatest.
OL,11,F"He was a glider, rather than a
OL,12,Fsidestepper, who had a subtle change
OL,13,Fof pace and direction. Coming on top
OL,14,Fof the recent deaths of Brian Price
OL,15,Fand JPR Williams, this is another huge
OL,16,Fblow for Welsh rugby.
